This app also have a other problems:

1.  Accessibility text not translated https://github.com/symfony/symfony-demo/blob/81797b9/app/Resources/views/base.html.twig#L45
2.  Missing text description for the text.
https://github.com/symfony/symfony-demo/blob/81797b9/app/Resources/views/base.html.twig#L79

    Example:
    ````
    <span class="sr-only">{{ 'choose.language' | trans }}</span>
    ````
    Class `sr-only` is a Bootstrap class. You can read more about in on: http://getbootstrap.com/components/#callout-glyphicons-accessibility
